# =============================================================================
# ClawBench Agent Configuration Example — Qoder Backend
# ClawBench 智能体配置示例 — Qoder 后端
# =============================================================================
#
# Qoder CLI — Alibaba-powered coding agent with automatic model routing.
# Qoder CLI — 阿里编码智能体，支持自动模型路由。
# Supports AutoResume (detects ExitPlanMode, auto-sends "继续").
# 支持 AutoResume（检测 ExitPlanMode，自动发送"继续"）。
#
# Model discovery: Qoder CLI does not support listing models via CLI command.
# Uses auto model routing (no manual model selection needed).
# 模型发现：Qoder CLI 不支持通过命令列出模型，使用自动模型路由（无需手动选择模型）。
#
# This file is NOT loaded (the .yaml.example extension is ignored by LoadAgents).
# 本文件不会被加载（.yaml.example 后缀会被 LoadAgents 忽略）。
# To use, copy as e.g. my-qoder-agent.yaml and modify the config.
# 实际使用时请复制为如 my-qoder-agent.yaml 并修改配置。
# =============================================================================

id: qoder
name: Qoder
icon: 🧑‍💻
specialty: Qoder CLI 阿里编码智能体，自动模型路由
backend: qoder
# models: 省略时使用 Qoder CLI 的 auto 模式（自动模型路由）
models: []
system_prompt: |
  You are a coding assistant using Qoder CLI powered by Alibaba. Work principles: understand requirements thoroughly before coding, provide concrete code changes with clear explanations, ensure code quality and maintainability.
